headline: Does the Antitrust Probe Signal Opportunity for Deere Stock in 2025?
summary: If you're standing at the crossroads wondering what to do with Deere stock, you're not alone. Investors have seen Deere’s share price serve up a mix of thrills and head-scratchers lately. After a modest lift of 2.7% this past week, the stock is still clawing back from a minor 2.3% drop over the last month. But push the lens wider and the growth story stands out. Deere is up 9.6% year-to-date, climbing 13.8% over the past year and an impressive 104.2% in five years. Those are numbers most...
